8DrPoh8x50HCJBqXxYfr6jR6t.jpg","original_title":"The Air He Breathes","original_language":"en"},{"id":46169,"adult":false,"title":"Twitches Too","video":false,"overview":"Reunited witch twins Camryn and Alex adjust to their new life as supernatural beings while at the same time trying to maintain a normal existence in this sequel to the magical Disney Channel original movie Twitches. But they soon find themselves going head to head with the forces of darkness that threaten to destroy their world. Luckily, their birth mother, the powerful Miranda, is on hand to help out.","genre_ids":[18,10751,14,10770],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0991,"vote_count":363,"poster_path":"/70aurzbqFMuJnwhIVW2aXeyzBAp.jpg","release_date":"2007-10-12","vote_average":6.672,"backdrop_path":"/siidi1AD6JNwWqrepY5DhqCCuEX.jpg","original_title":"Twitches Too","original_language":"en"},{"id":983683,"adult":false,"title":"Bill Burr Presents: Friends Who Kill","video":false,"overview":"In a night of killer comedy, Bill Burr hosts a showcase of his most raucous stand-up comic pals as they riff on everything from COVID to Michael Jackson.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4404,"vote_count":80,"poster_path":"/9gSpgNwjP3Qg8LAsrBgo1Fu6QdL.jpg","release_date":"2022-06-06","vote_average":5.356,"backdrop_path":"/2GFxMsZTiSU7i3GtwRnonx14nrb.jpg","original_title":"Bill Burr Presents: Friends Who Kill","original_language":"en"},{"id":29514,"adult":false,"title":"Two Evil Eyes","video":false,"overview":"A duo of Edgar Allan Poe adaptations about a greedy wife's attempt to embezzle her dying husband's fortune, and a sleazy reporter's adoption of a strange black cat.","genre_ids":[27],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.0374,"vote_count":324,"poster_path":"/zVWaQfaSZ7AWE0XqbMT57szVmXo.jpg","release_date":"1990-01-25","vote_average":6.133,"backdrop_path":"/wWucXwUmJiA5iUNqegJHbcy2Mzy.jpg","original_title":"Due occhi diabolici","original_language":"en"},{"id":541524,"adult":false,"title":"Passing","video":false,"overview":"In 1920s New York City, a Black woman finds her world upended when her life becomes intertwined with a former childhood friend who's passing as white.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.829,"vote_count":333,"poster_path":"/t4tYUT1oSWOP6XKZBoclPAG96KP.jpg","release_date":"2021-10-27","vote_average":6.285,"backdrop_path":"/7mH9nwyEyiGrODuq1khFEXyk5iY.jpg","original_title":"Passing","original_language":"en"},{"id":522892,"adult":false,"title":"Escaping the Madhouse: The Nellie Bly Story","video":false,"overview":"An investigative reporter Nellie Bly, who’s on a mission to expose the deplorable conditions and mistreatment of patients at the notorious Women’s Lunatic Asylum, and feigns mental illness in order to be institutionalized to report from the inside. The movie is an account of actual events surrounding Nellie’s stay beginning after she has undergone treatment, leaving her with no recollection of how she came to the asylum or her real identity.","genre_ids":[53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6532,"vote_count":135,"poster_path":"/h9LRcrTDtc9Vehv6wC0iuA4CiMg.jpg","release_date":"2019-01-06","vote_average":7.5,"backdrop_path":"/dTHQdxr0GqB88j47wAAAzE11hv1.jpg","original_title":"Escaping the Madhouse: The Nellie Bly Story","original_language":"en"},{"id":431135,"adult":false,"title":"Eva","video":false,"overview":"A playwright encounters a mysterious woman when he takes shelter in a chalet during a violent snowstorm and becomes obsessed with her.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7719,"vote_count":117,"poster_path":"/iDIQvVf8ZyAxf3WzJhbn15hpXPK.jpg","release_date":"2018-03-07","vote_average":4.4,"backdrop_path":"/qQwAHuJSY0zbXmSXNzOAL4Mm7uz.jpg","original_title":"Eva","original_language":"fr"},{"id":986097,"adult":false,"title":"HIM","video":false,"overview":"After suffering a potentially career-ending brain trauma, Cameron Cade receives a lifeline when his hero, legendary eight-time Championship quarterback and cultural megastar Isaiah White, offers to train Cam at Isaiah's isolated compound that he shares with his celebrity influencer wife. But as Cam's training accelerates, Isaiah's charisma begins to curdle into something darker.","genre_ids":[27,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.3208,"vote_count":319,"poster_path":"/qPJzcYR2f1O1uynYBCVPPJuOiAH.jpg","release_date":"2025-09-18","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":"/jzzpCJWkVZZwAxzzLmtYN0MBWFd.jpg","original_title":"HIM","original_language":"en"},{"id":764686,"adult":false,"title":"The Divide","video":false,"overview":"Raf and Julie, a couple on the verge of breaking up, find themselves in an emergency ward bordering on collapse on the evening of a Parisian Yellow Vest protest. Their encounter with Yann, an angry and injured demonstrator, will shatter each person's certainties and prejudices. Outside, the tension escalates.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.8981,"vote_count":174,"poster_path":"/ymHLBkyX7TpYyJLSIyHswrMjQgc.jpg","release_date":"2021-10-27","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/9bAwRoTEjXf7nnSnFr79jBtMhKw.jpg","original_title":"La Fracture","original_language":"fr"},{"id":402693,"adult":false,"title":"100 Meters","video":false,"overview":"Based on the incredibly true story of a Spanish man with Multiple Sclerosis who tried to finish an Iron-Man: 3,8km swimming, 180km cycling and 42 running. And he was told that he could not make 100 meters.","genre_ids":[35,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.2616,"vote_count":304,"poster_path":"/uqrRtRwH4qNMYA1xKTGLD9kvKK1.jpg","release_date":"2016-11-04","vote_average":7.365,"backdrop_path":"/eduYYQSmT4NLQlNhsrU9BdSPTFm.jpg","original_title":"100 metros","original_language":"es"},{"id":24913,"adult":false,"title":"April Fool's Day","video":false,"overview":"As soon as Muffy St. John and her college friends arrive on her parents' secluded island, someone starts trimming the guest list... one murder at a time.","genre_ids":[27,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7659,"vote_count":374,"poster_path":"/zNx2tNRzRyPsBSHX1VF2c7U0UyW.jpg","release_date":"1986-03-27","vote_average":6,"backdrop_path":"/lLxz3D3LBhyO3q9F0eBqSjepoD4.jpg","original_title":"April Fool's Day","original_language":"en"},{"id":1278263,"adult":false,"title":"The Seed of the Sacred Fig","video":false,"overview":"Investigating judge Iman grapples with paranoia amid political unrest in Tehran. When his gun vanishes, he suspects his wife and daughters, imposing draconian measures that strain family ties as societal rules crumble.","genre_ids":[18,53,80],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.7784,"vote_count":426,"poster_path":"/ifOazNzv2cNJ5CQjMV7cPXG2Lmy.jpg","release_date":"2024-09-18","vote_average":7.562,"backdrop_path":"/zqZzYVE4DWv92xrYSCEELPcLnUP.jpg","original_title":"Les Graines du figuier sauvage","original_language":"fr"},{"id":797394,"adult":false,"title":"Secret Magic Control Agency","video":false,"overview":"The Secret Magic Control Agency sends its two best agents, Hansel and Gretel, to fight against the witch of the Gingerbread House.","genre_ids":[16,35,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1096,"vote_count":391,"poster_path":"/4ZSzEDVdxWVMVO4oZDvoodQOEfr.jpg","release_date":"2021-03-18","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/tzJZaglq1hR7RS35BKG68Xz7KY0.jpg","original_title":"Ганзель, Гретель и Агентство Магии","original_language":"ru"},{"id":767499,"adult":false,"title":"The Manor","video":false,"overview":"After suffering a stroke, Judith moves into a historic nursing home, where she begins to suspect something supernatural is preying on the residents. With no one willing to believe her, Judith must either escape the confines of the manor, or fall victim to the evil that dwells within it.","genre_ids":[27,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.7752,"vote_count":299,"poster_path":"/eNf7Dp1m6eTKDY7p56iZdterZkL.jpg","release_date":"2021-10-08","vote_average":5.512,"backdrop_path":"/7k7U0XWjo5LRAu9UxF9iGE3pCrF.jpg","original_title":"The Manor","original_language":"en"},{"id":54320,"adult":false,"title":"Love","video":false,"overview":"After losing contact with Earth, Astronaut Lee Miller becomes stranded in orbit alone aboard the International Space Station. As time passes and life support systems dwindle, Lee battles to maintain his sanity - and simply stay alive. His world is a claustrophobic and lonely existence, until he makes a strange discovery aboard the ship.","genre_ids":[18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.4885,"vote_count":230,"poster_path":"/ghKqC61MuwJIY8Wh61258fxpcRV.jpg","release_date":"2011-02-02","vote_average":5.509,"backdrop_path":"/17yZ1T3lNc8ud80723vFyXwI1Iy.jpg","original_title":"Love","original_language":"en"},{"id":41471,"adult":false,"title":"Lone Wolf and Cub: Sword of Vengeance","video":false,"overview":"Official Shogunate executioner Ogami Itto has been framed for disloyalty to the Shogunate by the Yagyu clan, against whom he now is waging a one-man war, along with his infant son, Daigoro.","genre_ids":[18,28,12],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.2925,"vote_count":245,"poster_path":"/uxJJIzw3lDM0RbFQMQsTTRyFO2D.jpg","release_date":"1972-01-15","vote_average":7.359,"backdrop_path":"/r6kZzTqPxaiqpLTJdDJzgItz5bf.jpg","original_title":"子連れ狼 子を貸し腕貸しつかまつる","original_language":"ja"},{"id":572125,"adult":false,"title":"The 2019 Rose Parade with Cord & Tish","video":false,"overview":"Cord Hosenbeck and Tish Cattigan return for their annual round of live Rose Parade coverage. Cord Hosenbeck and Tish Cattigan are no strangers to the iconic New Year’s tradition of the Rose Parade, having covered the event for the past twenty-six years. After a whirlwind year that included traveling abroad to cover the Royal Wedding, the duo are more excited than ever to return to Pasadena. The esteemed Tim Meadows will also return for the festivities.","genre_ids":[35],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3174,"vote_count":24,"poster_path":"/11Qv