ju35EvGD.jpg","original_title":"Dr Terror's House of Horrors","original_language":"en"}],"similar_content":[{"id":853760,"adult":false,"title":"Ala Kachuu – Take and Run","video":false,"overview":"A young Kyrgyz woman is kidnapped and forced to marry. A drama about the desire for freedom in the clutches of a tradition.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":1.9804,"vote_count":14,"poster_path":"/mGGbm8IYURvkriTM924DoSCprBH.jpg","release_date":"2020-08-04","vote_average":7.3,"backdrop_path":"/jpeSfHKESQb052icUZzyE5hZabG.jpg","original_title":"Ala kachuu","original_language":"ky"},{"id":854084,"adult":false,"title":"Resemblance","video":false,"overview":"Dirk discovers something from his past that haunts him. He tries to use his skills to help him escape the guilt that he feels.","genre_ids":[18],"popularity":2.1661,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"2019-06-06","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Resemblance","original_language":"en"},{"id":462627,"adult":false,"title":"Homing In","video":false,"overview":"After a long day at work, Cal drives home to his suburban neighborhood and realizes that he accidentally went inside the wrong house. Inspired by true events of Levittown, NY; American's first suburb.","genre_ids":[18,10751,9648],"popularity":1.1019,"vote_count":2,"poster_path":"/d08POGAeX7QbKQeYcvK9D3YvtVN.jpg","release_date":"2017-07-01","vote_average":6.5,"backdrop_path":"/3VbeonyFF8NbM5FuCf4t2Q7CrpF.jpg","original_title":"Homing In","original_language":"en"},{"id":256,"adult":false,"title":"Antoine and Colette","video":false,"overview":"Now aged 17, Antoine Doinel works in a factory which makes records. At a music concert, he meets a girl his own age, Colette, and falls in love with her. Later, Antoine goes to extraordinary lengths to please his new girlfriend and her parents, but Colette still only regards him as a casual friend. First segment of “Love at Twenty” (1962).","genre_ids":[10749,18,35],"popularity":0.7516,"vote_count":273